neo F.C.|Borneo]]{{efn|Joined on 7 January 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Rekrut Diky Indriyana Sebagai Penjaga Gawang |url=http://borneofc.id/news.php?id=3302 |website=borneofc.id |accessdate=7 January 2020}}</ref>}} || rowspan=\"2\"| <ref>{{cite web |title=MATUR SUKSMA! BALI UNITED RESMI MELEPAS DIKY INDRIYANA DAN PUTU PAGER |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/matur-suksma-bali-united-resmi-melepas-diky-indriyana-dan-putu-pager/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=29 December 2019 |date=29 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| GK || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[I Putu Pager Wirajaya]] || [[Mitra Kukar F.C.|Mitra Kukar]]{{efn|Joined on 22 February 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Pemain Lama & Kiper Dipastikan Perkuat Mitra Kukar Musim 2020, Jafri Sastra: Kita Masih Punya Waktu |url=https://kaltim.tribunnews.com/2020/02/23/pemain-lama-kiper-dipastikan-perkuat-mitra-kukar-musim-2020-jafri-sastra-kita-masih-punya-waktu?page=all |website=Tribun Kaltim |accessdate=6 March 2020 |language=id-ID}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 30 December 2019 || MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[I Nyoman Sukarja]] || [[Free agent]] || Released || rowspan=\"2\"| <ref>{{cite web |title=MATUR SUKSMA! BALI UNITED RESMI LEPAS NYOMAN SUKARJA DAN ALDINO HERDIANTO |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/matur-suksma-bali-united-resmi-lepas-nyoman-sukarja-dan-aldino-herdianto/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=30 December 2019 |date=30 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| FW || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Aldino Herdianto]] || [[Badak Lampung F.C.|Badak Lampung]]{{efn|Joined on 15 January 2020.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kastara |first1=Bintang |title=Eks-Striker Bali United Resmi Gabung Klub Liga 2 |url=https://www.bolanusantara.com/news/eks-striker-bali-united-resmi-gabung-klub-liga-2 |website=Eks-Striker Bali United Resmi Gabung Klub Liga 2 |accessdate=15 January 2020 |language=id}}</ref>}} || rowspan=\"3\"| Free transfer\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 31 December 2019 || FW || {{flagicon|Indonesia}}