li United Official Website |accessdate=28 December 2019 |date=28 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 29 December 2019 || GK || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Nadeo Argawinata]] || [[Borneo F.C.|Borneo]] || rowspan=\"3\"| Undisclosed || <ref>{{cite web |title=TERBARU! NADEO ARGAWINATA RESMI JADI KIPER ANYAR BALI UNITED |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/terbaru-nadeo-argawinata-resmi-jadi-kiper-anyar-bali-united/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=29 December 2019 |date=29 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 31 December 2019 || FW || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Muhammad Rahmat]] || [[PSM Makassar|PSM]] || <ref>{{cite web |title=TERBARU! MUHAMMAD RAHMAT RESMI TAMBAH AMUNISI PENYERANG SAYAP BALI UNITED |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/terbaru-muhammad-rahmat-resmi-tambah-amunisi-penyerang-sayap-bali-united/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=31 December 2019 |date=31 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 5 January 2020 || FW || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Lerby Eliandry]] || [[Borneo F.C.|Borneo]] || <ref>{{cite web |title=BALIKAN! LERBY ELIANDRY \"KEMBALI\" JADI BAGIAN SKUAD SERDADU TRIDATU |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/balikan-lerby-eliandry-kembali-jadi-bagian-skuad-serdadu-tridatu/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=5 January 2020 |date=5 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 6 January 2020 || MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Sidik Saimima]] || [[PSS Sleman|PSS]] || Free transfer || <ref>{{cite web |title=TERBARU! SIDIK SAIMIMA JADI REKRUTAN TERBARU SERDADU TRIDATU! |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/terbaru-sidik-saimima-jadi-rekrutan-terbaru-serdadu-tridatu/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=6 January 2020 |date=6 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 12 January 2020 || MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Reza Irfana]] || rowspan=\"3\"| [[Bali United F.C. Youth Sector|Youth sector]] || rowspan=\"3\"| Promoted || rowspan=\"2\"| <ref>{{cite web |title=TERBARU! REZA IRFANA DAN KADEK HAARLEM RESMI JADI BAGIAN TIM SENIOR BALI UNITED |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/terbaru-reza-irfana-dan-kadek-haarlem-resmi-jadi-bagian-tim-senior-bali-united/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=12 January 2020 |date=12 January 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Kadek Haarlem Anggariva]]\n|-\n| 22 February 2020 || FW || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Irfan Jauhari]] || <ref>{{cite web |title=RESMI! IRFAN JAUHARI DIKONTRAK UNTUK SKUAD BALI UNITED SENIOR |url=https://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/resmi-irfan-jauhari-dikontrak-untuk-skuad-bali-united-senior/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=22 February 2020 |date=22 February 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Transfers out ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Date\n! Pos.\n! Name\n! To\n! Fee\n! Ref.\n|-\n| 27 December 2019 || MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Ahmad Agung]] || [[PSM Makassar|PSM]]{{efn|Joined on 8 January 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Appi : Tanggal 10 Hussein El Dor Tiba di Makassar |url=https://celebesmedia.id/psm/artikel/1014080120/appi-tanggal-10-hussein-el-dor-tiba-di-makassar |website=celebesmedia.id |accessdate=8 January 2020 |language=en}}</ref>}} || rowspan=\"5\"| Free transfer || <ref>{{cite web |title=MATUR SUKSMA! BALI UNITED RESMI LEPAS AHMAD AGUNG SETIA BUDI |url=http://www.baliutd.com/news/media-news/matur-suksma-bali-united-resmi-lepas-ahmad-agung-setia-budi/ |website=Bali United Official Website |accessdate=27 December 2019 |date=27 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 28 December 2019 || MF || {{flagicon|Indonesia}} [[Ahmad Maulana Putra]] || [[Semen Padang F.C.|Semen Padang]]{{efn|Joined on 27 February 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=Pelatih Semen Padang FC: 25 Pemain Saat Ini Sudah Cukup |url=https://langgam.id/pelatih-semen-padang-fc-25-pemain-saat-ini-sudah-cukup/ |website=Langgam.id |accessdate=6 March 2020 |language=id-ID |date=3 March 2020}}</ref>}} || rowspan=\"2\"| <ref>{{cite web |title=MATUR SUKSMA! BALI UNITED RESMI LEPAS AHMAD MAULANA DAN NYOMAN ADI PARWA |