esian}}</ref>\n|-\n| \n| [[Defender (association football)|DF]]\n| {{Flagicon|South Korea}} [[Ha Dae-Won]]\n| {{Flagicon|IDN}} [[Bali United]]\n| Released\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Kerangkan Skuad Bali United Bentukan Indra Sjafri Mulai Terbentuk|url=http://www.tribunnews.com/superball/2015/01/11/kerangkan-skuad-bali-united-bentukan-indra-sjafri-mulai-terbentuk|accessdate=13 January 2015|language=Indonesian}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== Sources ==\n\n{{Empty section|date=January 2015}}\n\n== External links ==\n\n\n\n[[Category:Indonesian football clubs 2015 season|PS Barito Putera]]\n[[Category:PS Barito Putera]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football club season\n| club               = [[Barito Putera]]\n| season             = 2015\n| manager            = [[Salahudin (born 1970)|Salahuddin]]\n| mgrtitle           = Head Coach\n| chairman           = H.A. Sulaiman.H.B\n| stadium            = [[17 May Stadium|17 May]]\n| league             = [[Indonesian Super League]]\n| league result      = TBD\n| league topscorer   = \n| season topscorer   = \n| highest attendance = \n| lowest attendance  = \n| average attendance = \n| prevseason         = [[2014 PS Barito Putera season|2014]]\n| nextseason         = [[2016 PS Barito Putera season|2016]]\n}}\n\n== Review and events ==\n\n=== Pre\u20132015 ===\n\n== Matches ==\n\n=== Legend ===\n{{legend2|#CCFFCC|Win|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFFFCC|Draw|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#FFCCCC|Loss|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#CCCCCC|Postponed|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n\n=== Friendlies ===\n\n=== Indonesia Super League ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" Style=\"text-align: center;font-size:75%\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:100px\"| Date\n!rowspan=\"2\"| {{Tooltip|KO|Kickoff time}}\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Stadium\n!rowspan=\"2\"| City\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Opponent\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Result{{ref|a|4}}\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Attendance\n!colspan=\"2\"| Goalscorers\n!rowspan=\"2\"| Source\n|-\n! style=\"wi